{"id": "e68d9c0b-c295-40c7-a778-d1a335a19f3d", "task_id": "a9bd1a86-2c34-471e-af33-820d1017b32d", "path": "templates/index.html", "artifact_type": "file", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>TERMINAL ACCESS | Cyber-Pulse</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --neon-cyan: #00f3ff;\n            --neon-magenta: #ff00ff;\n            --bg-dark: #0a0a0c;\n            --bg-accent: #1a1a2e;\n            --glitch-speed: 3s;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: var(--bg-dark);\n            color: var(--neon-cyan);\n            height: 100vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            perspective: 1000px;\n        }\n\n        /* Scanline Overlay */\n        body::before {\n            content: \" \";\n            display: block;\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0; left: 0; bottom: 0; right: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(18, 16, 16, 0) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 50%), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.06), rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.02), rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.06));\n            z-index: 20;\n            background-size: 100% 4px, 3px 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n\n        .grid-bg {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;\n            background-image: \n                linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),\n                linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);\n            background-size: 40px 40px;\n            z-index: -1;\n            transform: rotateX(45deg);\n            animation: moveGrid 20s linear infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes moveGrid {\n            from { background-position: 0 0; }\n            to { background-position: 0 1000px; }\n        }\n\n        .login-card {\n            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8);\n            padding: 3rem;\n            border: 2px solid var(--neon-cyan);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-cyan), inset 0 0 10px var(--neon-cyan);\n            width: 400px;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%);\n        }\n\n        .login-card::after {\n            content: \"VER: 2.0.77\";\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: 5px;\n            right: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.6rem;\n            opacity: 0.7;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 2rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 5px;\n            position: relative;\n            animation: glitch-text var(--glitch-speed) infinite;\n        }\n\n        h1::before, h1::after {\n            content: attr(data-text);\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;\n        }\n\n        h1::before {\n            left: 2px;\n            text-shadow: -2px 0 var(--neon-magenta);\n            clip: rect(44px, 450px, 56px, 0);\n            animation: glitch-anim 5s infinite linear alternate-reverse;\n        }\n\n        h1::after {\n            left: -2px;\n            text-shadow: -2px 0 var(--neon-cyan);\n            clip: rect(44px, 450px, 56px, 0);\n            animation: glitch-anim2 1s infinite linear alternate-reverse;\n        }\n\n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            font-size: 0.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        input {\n            width: 100%;\n            background: transparent;\n            border: 1px solid var(--neon-cyan);\n            padding: 10px;\n            color: white;\n            outline: none;\n            transition: 0.3s;\n        }\n\n        input:focus {\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-cyan);\n            background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            background: transparent;\n            border: 1px solid var(--neon-magenta);\n            color: var(--neon-magenta);\n            cursor: pointer;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: 0.3s;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .btn:hover {\n            background: var(--neon-magenta);\n            color: white;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--neon-magenta);\n        }\n\n        .status-msg {\n            margin-top: 1.5rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px dashed;\n        }\n\n        .status-msg.error {\n            color: #ff4d4d;\n            border-color: #ff4d4d;\n            animation: shake 0.5s;\n        }\n\n        .status-msg.success {\n            color: #4dff88;\n            border-color: #4dff88;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-anim {\n          0% { clip: rect(31px, 9999px, 94px, 0); }\n          20% { clip: rect(62px, 9999px, 42px, 0); }\n          40% { clip: rect(16px, 9999px, 78px, 0); }\n          60% { clip: rect(87px, 9999px, 12px, 0); }\n          80% { clip: rect(5px, 9999px, 51px, 0); }\n          100% { clip: rect(44px, 9999px, 92px, 0); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch-anim2 {\n          0% { clip: rect(70px, 9999px, 20px, 0); }\n          20% { clip: rect(10px, 9999px, 80px, 0); }\n          40% { clip: rect(40px, 9999px, 60px, 0); }\n          60% { clip: rect(20px, 9999px, 90px, 0); }\n          80% { clip: rect(60px, 9999px, 30px, 0); }\n          100% { clip: rect(30px, 9999px, 70px, 0); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes shake {\n            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }\n            25% { transform: translateX(-5px); }\n            75% { transform: translateX(5px); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"grid-bg\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"login-card\">\n        <h1 data-text=\"SYSTEM ACCESS\">SYSTEM ACCESS</h1>\n        \n        <form action=\"/login\" method=\"POST\">\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label>USER_ID // NET_RUNNER</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" required placeholder=\"IDENTITY...\" autocomplete=\"off\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"form-group\">\n                <label>ENCRYPTION_KEY // SECURE</label>\n                <input type=\"password\" name=\"password\" required placeholder=\"********\" autocomplete=\"off\">\n            </div>\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn\">EXECUTE_AUTH</button>\n        </form>\n\n        {% if message %}\n        <div class=\"status-msg {{ status }}\">\n            {{ message }}\n        </div>\n        {% endif %}\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // Subtle effect: Random text flicker for titles\n        const h1 = document.querySelector('h1');\n        const original = h1.innerText;\n        const chars = \"ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ1234567890@#$%^&*\";\n        \n        function randomGlitch() {\n            let iterations = 0;\n            const interval = setInterval(() => {\n                h1.innerText = h1.innerText.split(\"\")\n                    .map((letter, index) => {\n                        if(index < iterations) return original[index];\n                        return chars[Math.floor(Math.random() * 44)];\n                    })\n                    .join(\"\");\n                \n                if(iterations >= original.length) clearInterval(interval);\n                iterations += 1/3;\n            }, 30);\n        }\n\n        // Glitch effect on card entrance\n        window.onload = randomGlitch;\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "patches": [], "metadata": {"language": "html", "framework": "static_html", "explanation": "A high-fidelity cyberpunk login page featuring CSS-based glitch effects, neon cyan/magenta color palette, scanline overlays, and a retro-grid background. The form is configured to POST data to the '/login' endpoint using standard form encoding. It also includes Jinja2 template logic to display feedback messages ('ACCESS GRANTED' or 'ACCESS DENIED') with corresponding CSS classes for success or error styling. Vanilla JS adds a minor 'decrypting' text effect on page load for immersion.", "dependencies": []}, "created_at": "2026-05-17 13:27:01.445252"}